text: This was the first edition of the tournament. Wishaya Trongcharoenchaikul and Kittipong Wachiramanowong won the title after defeating Sanchai and Sonchat Ratiwatana 7–6(11–9), 6–3 in the final. ==Seeds== ==Draw== ==References== * Main Draw Wind Energy Holding Bangkok Open - Doubles
